summary: This is a calendar entry scheduling the start of jury selection for the Ghislaine Maxwell trial, set to begin on November 15, 2021, with an alarm reminder set for 18 hours prior.

events.title: Maxwell Jury Selection Start
events.description: Scheduled start date for jury selection in the Ghislaine Maxwell trial.

keyFacts: Jury selection for Ghislaine Maxwell's trial was scheduled to begin on November 15, 2021.
The calendar entry was created on May 11, 2021, and last modified on August 27, 2021.
An alarm was set to display a reminder 18 hours before the scheduled start of jury selection.
